channel.title: Shuru Lab
channel.description: "Greetings, fellow science enthusiasts! Welcome to the wittiest and most experimental engineering lab on the block. Where we take the laws of physics, turn them upside down, and create things you never thought were possible. So grab your lab coat, goggles, and a sense of humor, because things are about to get wild and hilarious in the lab!"
